title: Moon & Sun "Hibernate" - Converse Red Light Sessions
description: The haunting, Caribbean influenced vibes of Moon & Sun perfectly matched the atmosphere inside Amsterdam’s ‘Waag’ as they performed ‘Hibernate’. Originally the old city gate and anatomical theatre, this gloomy venue is full of history and secrets.
